176 A.3d 214 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. RAKEEM SCOTT, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-379 September Term 2017

080169 November 30, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004173-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
